Speaker 1: Hello?

Speaker 1: Okay, David Myers in New London, Wisconsin?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Cancel it, please.

Speaker 1: Okay, all right, you're good to go.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.
